<plot>The complete, unabridged history of the Chinese people in Hawaii. Featuring stories of men like Chun Ah Fong (Hawaii's Chinese Merchant Prince), Sun Yat Sen (the Father of Modern China) and Hiram Fong (the First Asian U.S. Senator), this exclusive documentary examines the lives, stories and social impact of Hawaii's Chinese immigrants and their modern descendants.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?195089</url></doc>
